steps.name: user types "Mahendra" in data owner name and select one of the suggestion
select "Direct" and "To IMS" from the drop down
select "2016-11-03" from the Transfer schedule text box
select schedule from the "Daily" drop down.

user is able to navigate to Activation Details tab
select Activate Immediate check box
uncheck no end date check box
enter the "2016-11-18"

user is on Modify org page
click on Data Transfer tab
list of data transfer should be displayed and status as Active.
